    {
      "id": "1b14750c-f3ba-8009-a0d7-ccd0010e0c7d",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The work is conduct using data available in the platform Naviance, which stores the information about colleges their users wish to go to. The results show that students using the platform are more likely to apply to colleges for which they are generally over-qualified and less likely to apply to colleges whose average qualifications are superiro to the student’s own qualification.",
